        "grammarPoints": {
            "heading": "语法要点 Grammar points",
            "notes": [
                {
                    "title": "名词修饰名词",
                    "content": [
                        "1. 名词可以直接修饰名词，如：the hotel manager's office",
                        "2. 其他例子：telephone number（电话号码）, village fair（乡村集市）",
                        "3. the fair of the village = the fair in the village"
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "title": "feel + 形容词",
                    "content": [
                        "1. feel + 形容词一般指心情'觉得……，感觉到……'",
                        "2. feel upset 表示'心烦意乱，很苦恼'",
                        "3. 类似用法：feel happy, feel sad, feel excited"
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "title": "表示'丢失'的多种表达",
                    "content": [
                        "1. lose sth. / sth. be lost - 丢失（一般用于物品）",
                        "2. sth. is missing - 丢失的（可用于人和物）",
                        "3. sth. is gone - 不见了",
                        "4. sth./sb. disappear/disappeared - 消失了"
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
